# Ajuda Cart Batch Selector

## Installation

1. Make sure you have [Tampermonkey](https://www.tampermonkey.net/) installed
2. [Click here to install the script](https://greasyfork.org/en/scripts/550365-ajuda-cart-batch-selector)
3. Click the green "Install this script" button
4. Click "Install" when Tampermonkey opens
5. Refresh your Ajuda page

## Features
- Remembers your last vertical and function selections
- Supports primary and secondary batch selection
- Works with all major verticals and functions

## Usage
1. Navigate to the Ajuda cart page
2. Look for the new "Batch Selector" button
3. Click the button to open the selection dialog
4. Choose your vertical and function
5. Select either "Primary Batch" or "Secondary Batch"
6. The script will automatically select the appropriate items in your cart
